# msg-patterns.list — banned-pattern template for check-commit-msg / check-tree-terms.
# gate-sdk/SPEC.md §check-commit-msg. One grep -E pattern per line; '#' comments
# and blank lines are ignored. Copy to your gates dir as msg-patterns.list
# (tracked, generic) and keep private term lists in msg-patterns.local.list
# (gitignored). Any file named msg-patterns* is self-exempt from check-tree-terms.

# Absolute home paths — leak the local filesystem layout into a public surface.
/(home|Users)/[A-Za-z0-9._-]+

# The Claude Code promo URL — the marketing link that ends a generated PR body.
# The Co-Authored-By trailer is a footer convention, not a leak: do not ban it.
claude\.com/claude-code

# Session-reference class — a harness-injected trailer referencing an internal
# session, before it lands in public history. The session-share URL host (public
# software's public domain, so a shape not a private term); and a trailer-shaped
# 'Key: ' line carrying a full UUID — the session-id trailer shape whatever key
# the harness uses. The UUID half is trailer-anchored so it matches an injected
# footer, never a synthetic session UUID that check-tree-terms scans in smoke/.
claude\.ai/
^[A-Za-z][A-Za-z-]*: .*[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{12}
